{"tid":1416996,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武義士全部同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T05:43:18.000Z","uid":286135,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2fdcb3ac75ace174156fafd3728dd78d7714008","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:01.000Z","msg":"多謝各位勇武派既付出<br />\n小弟<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">衷心感謝</span></span>你地<br />\n但係係時候休息下，你地好勇敢<br />\n<br />\n我係P牌仔，但係絕對唔係鬼，唔係分化撚<br />\n我絕對不分化，不篤灰，不割席<br />\n<br />\n但係希望可以討論下以後既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">活動方針</span></span><br />\n我認為第一個死線期限就係9月開學，開學之後學生既時間會變少<br />\n要係9月前做第一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後衝刺</span></span><br />\n我見到有人要成立<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民間記者會</span></span>，希望可以大力推<br />\n並且係兩個星期內暫停大部分勇武行為，轉為閃擊戰<br />\n以及最好作為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民間記者會</span></span>既保鏢<br />\n以民間記者會既關注度壓過政府既記者會<br />\n文宣加大力度宣傳警察有69以來既各宗罪行<br />\n並將所有罪行向警察投訴科投訴，理所當然<br />\n政府既打壓下，警察絕對唔會比告入，或只以輕微罪行告入<br />\n並以警察不能以正當手法告入以及政府打壓投訴警察科等作宣傳方向<br />\n盡量為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武派</span></span>之後既行動<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">爭取民心</span></span>，<br />\n係兩個星期最後通牒後，政府無作出正面回應<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">五大訴求</span></strong></strong></span>後<br />\n就以最大限度升級勇武派武力，據我所知，有tg gp指出有新型武器正在研發<br />\n例如咩投咩石咩車如何量產，本人唔鼓吹任何暴力，所以唔好搞爛警車玻璃窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係唔代表勇武派唔出動，而係唔主動出擊，例如佔路等<br />\n不過本人都唔鼓吹任何挑釁警犬既行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為佢會主動出擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而令勇武有反擊理由<br />\n以及比和理非有喘息空間，以及向和理非預告未來升級行動，目標係下次警民衝突<br />\n每人最少都有個6502+2097既防毒面具，同埋高級護目鏡<br />\n不過我都唔鼓吹有警察濫捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，市民去圍警處呢個行為因為會令到警察好無面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫我推上去並加以討論，可以插但係唔好太大力，多謝<br />\n利伸：夢中催煙吸引機，唔知點解每次發夢催煙都好近<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fb2ec6fa94c87b3e0ee5372598cb2861a2ccf1","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92e99343918fc7e3932702ab58e319bf482342ac","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21b545acb820b182c51b060779a70e3cf95a7feb","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b753022bc11868693c92724f81364a47c0bbe667","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好係升級行動燒左架水炮車，因為佢地會無水玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04f64bba8b0cd478e7a8e653800b79e969ef22d","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"644180cce0c9d31d58d6bcaab62dfe4af4e76eae","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"9baf974a3c60d3d43feae61f6738ca62c8d2218f","tid":1416996,"uid":286135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:41:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a507a782e318ec24c6013470cc5d25bd0c5f9f31","tid":1416996,"uid":64003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:43:18.000Z","msg":"［好臭喔］啲狗幾時會放屁 幾時會射尿？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420697</a>"}]}